data.title: Population: Census: Sichuan: Chengdu
data.meta_description: Population: Census: Sichuan: Chengdu data was reported at 20,937.757 Person th in Dec 2020. This records an increase from the previous number of 14,047.625 Person th for Dec 2010. Population: Census: Sichuan: Chengdu data is updated yearly, averaging 14,047.625 Person th (Median) from Dec 2000 to 2020, with 3 observations. The data reached an all-time high of 20,937.757 Person th in 2020 and a record low of 11,108.534 Person th in 2000. Population: Census: Sichuan: Chengdu data remains active status in CEIC and is reported by Chengdu Municipal Bureau of Statistics. The data is categorized under China Premium Database’s Socio-Demographic – Table CN.GE: Population: Prefecture Level City: By Census.
